videoDetails.Title: 11 Tips for Urban CQC in War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
There are lots of close-range, urban maps in War Thunder like Advance to the Rhine, Iberian Castle, and Sweden. These tips will help you dominate these maps, getting up close and personal with your enemy.

Disclaimer: Following these tips may lead to an increase in your win rate and K/D ratio, and cause many of your enemies to ragequit. The 27th Jägers is not liable for any silver and RP gained while following these tips.
